39:23.289 --> 39:25.809
Is the public defender
in orange county,

39:25.809 --> 39:27.526
And she went to law school with kevin.
No.

39:27.526 --> 39:30.509
Yes.
Oh, wow. What a small world.

39:30.509 --> 39:33.679
Yes, isn't it? (laughs)
and the funny thing is,

39:33.679 --> 39:35.648
She says she knows you
very well.

39:35.648 --> 39:37.215
Nora, whatever she said--

39:37.215 --> 39:40.674
And the two of you were
quite serious with each other,

39:40.674 --> 39:43.271
For a brief time
not too long ago.

39:43.271 --> 39:43.892
Just friends.

39:43.892 --> 39:47.224
Friends?
Or is she another investor?

39:47.224 --> 39:50.550
Ooh. The plot thickens.

39:50.550 --> 39:55.625
You are both very photogenic, might I add.
Maybe I should go.

39:55.625 --> 39:56.474
<i>Sit.</i>

39:59.353 --> 40:03.189
Marilyn invested
a very large sum of money

40:03.189 --> 40:05.051
In one of simon's causes

40:05.051 --> 40:07.876
And then woke up to an empty bed
and a big, empty bank account.
No.

40:09.574 --> 40:11.197
Nora, you're not
gonna believe this--

40:11.197 --> 40:12.352
You're right.
I don't believe it.

40:12.352 --> 40:16.211
You're a liar,
and somehow I didn't see it,

40:16.211 --> 40:18.838
Which is crazy, because I was
married to one for 40 years.

40:18.838 --> 40:21.719
(doorbell rings twice)

40:21.719 --> 40:25.014
Ooh. That's not marilyn weisman,is it, mom?
No, I don't think so.

40:25.014 --> 40:26.878
I think that's probably
detective tanner.

40:28.338 --> 40:30.076
You--you called the police?

40:30.076 --> 40:31.158
Marilyn did.

40:31.158 --> 40:34.725
Gosh, I'm so sorry about
those charges she's filed.

40:34.725 --> 40:36.408
(doorbell rings twice)

40:36.408 --> 40:39.106
Nora. Nora. Please--

40:39.106 --> 40:41.530
I really wouldn't keep
detective tanner waiting

40:41.530 --> 40:42.229
If I were you.

40:42.229 --> 40:43.034
Take a sandwich.

40:54.037 --> 40:55.244
(door opens and closes)

40:55.244 --> 40:56.416
(laughs) god.

40:56.416 --> 40:59.000
Mom, that was like--
that was incredible.

40:59.000 --> 41:00.457
You were like a bond girl.

41:00.457 --> 41:02.472
Not a bond girl.

41:02.472 --> 41:05.140
I was like bond,
not his girl.

41:05.140 --> 41:07.583
Nora, I was terrified
back there.
Aah!

41:07.583 --> 41:09.461
There's the bond girl.

41:09.461 --> 41:12.255
I called saul to come here
in case there was trouble.

41:12.255 --> 41:14.489
I had my finger
onhe alarm's panic button

41:14.489 --> 41:18.112
The whole time I was there.
(laughs)
mom, I am in awe of you.

41:18.112 --> 41:20.381
Well, sarah, you're not the only
one who knows how to google.

41:20.381 --> 41:21.687
You okay, sweetheart?

41:21.687 --> 41:25.911
Yes, I'm fine. I'm fine.
It was very satisfying.

41:25.911 --> 41:27.584
Saul, pass me my phone.
Who are you calling?

41:27.584 --> 41:29.316
Kitty. Come on.
Okay.

41:29.316 --> 41:30.774
This is the stuff
that legends are made of.
(laughs)

41:30.774 --> 41:34.355
Kit, it's sarah.
Listen, um, press conference.

41:34.355 --> 41:36.910
I'll wait while you get
everybody.

